Class DiscoveryDao

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.linkedpipes.lpa.backend.entities.database.DiscoveryDao
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    @Entity(name="discovery")
public class DiscoveryDao
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Record on discoveries and parameters used to start them. We record the time discovery was started and finished as well as SPARQL endpoint IRI, data sample IRI and list of named graphs. Discoveries are mapped onto user profile.
